title: Minneapolis app maker wins top MN Cup prize
text:
Home / News / Business & Economy / Minneapolis app maker wins top MN Cup prize Astropad co-founders Matt Ronge, left, and Giovanni Donelli claimed the top spot in this year’s MN Cup competition, a high-profile initiative to fund and build out Minnesota’s most promising startups. (Submitted photo: Astropad) Minneapolis app maker wins top MN Cup prize By: Karlee Weinmann September 10, 2015 2:38 pm 0 Astropad took top honors in the state’s top startup competition.
